metadata.name: Founders Collection #1/420
metadata.description: We are Onboard, and we are on a mission to revolutionize the world of action sports. And it all starts with you. Your voice will matter, your ideas will be heard, and your actions will make a difference. This is limited edition series of 420 NFTs that will give you access to the inner workings of Onboard and the power to shape the future of the industry. With this token, you'll be more than just a member of the crew - you'll be a key player in a movement that's changing the game. Claim yours now. Artwork will update once the Founders Token voting is complete. Virtual fist bump! üëäüèæ
